==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Monogyny
<hw>Mo*nog"y*ny</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Monogynia</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Marriage with the one woman
only.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The state or condition of being
monogynous.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Monohemerous</ent>⟦br⟧
